41:["$","p",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"TCP head-of-line blocking."}]," Packet loss on the satellite link causes audio freezes. We have a jitter buffer spec (50–200 ms) but have not implemented it. This is the most significant v1 limitation."]}]
42:["$","p",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"No forward error correction."}]," RTP typically carries FEC for voice. We don't implement FEC in v1. Phase 2 adds this alongside UDP."]}]
43:["$","p",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Mixed traffic on one socket."}]," Control messages (small, infrequent, need reliability) and audio (large, frequent, can tolerate loss) share the same WebSocket connection. They have different optimal transport characteristics. v2 separates them."]}]
